summary: Already when writing for a local newspaper as a teenager I noticed that copywriting is one of my biggest passions. Since then I focused on evolving and enhancing my skills to create impactful content. Working in marketing for several years I developed a customer-oriented mindset and implemented effective social media campaigns. Whether it is a snappy phrase, a sharp headline or a well-researched article, my copy is designed to engage customers on various platforms.
